type Contact @key(fields: "id") {
  displayName: String @external
  id: ID!
}

type ContactConnection {
  edges: [ContactEdge!]!
  nodes: [Contact!]! @provides(fields: "displayName")
  pageInfo: PageInfo!
  totalCount: Int!
  totalMatches: Int!
}

type ContactEdge {
  cursor: String!
  node: Contact! @provides(fields: "displayName")
}

type PageInfo {
  endCursor: String @shareable
  hasNextPage: Boolean! @shareable
  hasPreviousPage: Boolean! @shareable
  startCursor: String @shareable
}

type Query {
  contacts(after: String, before: String, first: Int, last: Int): ContactConnection! @provides(fields: "edges { node { displayName } }")
}
